title: Kimbella Interview and more
itunes:title: Kimbella Interview and more
description:
Today on the show we had Love and Hip Hop Kimbella stop by where she spoke about her beef with Yandy, not holding grudges and more. Also, Charlamagne, gave "Donkey of the Day" to Harvard University for telling students to move off campus in fear of the Corona Virus and Angela helped some listeners out during "Ask Yee".
